cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this methodology, please cite it as below."
title: "Agentic Architecture Audit"
abstract: >-
  A two-stage, evidence-first audit for AI-assisted codebases. A discovery pass
  records what a repository claims to be; an eleven-phase audit tests those claims
  with citations. The package contains two authority texts — a Project Profile
  Discovery Directive and an Agentic Architecture Audit Specification — plus
  derived companion documents.
